{
  "content": "<h1>一、 📝 行前备忘录</h1><h3><strong>重要文件（请务必带好）</strong></h3><ul class=\"ybc-ul-component\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>✅ <strong>护照</strong>：有效期需超过6个月，至少有2页空白页</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>✅ <strong>签证材料</strong>：免签入境需准备返程机票（30天内）、酒店订单</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>✅ <strong>证件复印件</strong>：护照个人信息页、签证页复印2份，与原件分开放</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>✅ <strong>机票行程单</strong>：打印或电子版保存在手机</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>✅ <strong>酒店预订单</strong>：包含入住人姓名、日期、地址</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>✅ <strong>旅行保险单</strong>：建议购买覆盖医疗、意外、行李的保险</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>📸 <strong>证件照</strong>：准备2张2寸白底照片备用</p></span></li></ul><h3><strong>衣物准备</strong></h3><div class=\"hyc-common-markdown__table-wrapper isDark\" data-has-scroll=\"false\"><table><thead><tr><th><p>场景</p></th><th><p>推荐衣物</p></th><th><p>特别提醒</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>日常游览</strong>​</p></td><td><p>轻便夏装、速干衣裤、防晒衣</p></td><td><p>清迈全年温暖，但寺庙需长袖长裤</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>寺庙参观</strong>​</p></td><td><p>过膝长裙/裤、有袖上衣、披肩</p></td><td><p>进入寺庙必须着装得体</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>山区活动</strong>​</p></td><td><p>薄外套、长裤、舒适登山鞋</p></td><td><p>因他农山等山区温差大</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>夜间出行</strong>​</p></td><td><p>薄长袖、长裤</p></td><td><p>防蚊虫，应对凉风</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>游泳/瀑布</strong>​</p></td><td><p>泳衣、速干毛巾、溯溪鞋</p></td><td><p>沾沾瀑布等景点需要</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h3><strong>洗漱与护肤</strong></h3><ul class=\"ybc-ul-component\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>🧴 <strong>基础护理</strong>：旅行装洗发水、沐浴露、牙膏牙刷</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>🧴 <strong>护肤必备</strong>：高倍防晒霜（SPF50+）、晒后修复、保湿霜</p><div class=\"hyc-common-markdown__table-wrapper isDark\" data-has-scroll=\"false\"><table><thead><tr><th><p>类型</p></th><th><p>推荐产品</p></th><th><p>使用场景</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>面部防晒</p></td><td><p>轻薄型防晒霜</p></td><td><p>日常外出</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>身体防晒</p></td><td><p>防水防汗型</p></td><td><p>户外活动、瀑布游玩</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>晒后修复</p></td><td><p>芦荟胶、修复霜</p></td><td><p>每晚使用</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>驱蚊产品</p></td><td><p>DEET含量20%以上</p></td><td><p>全天候，特别是傍晚</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div></span></li></ul><h3><strong>电子设备</strong></h3><div class=\"hyc-common-markdown__table-wrapper isDark\" data-has-scroll=\"false\"><table><thead><tr><th><p>设备</p></th><th><p>数量</p></th><th><p>备注</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>手机及充电器</p></td><td><p>1套</p></td><td><p>开通国际漫游或购买当地卡</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>充电宝</p></td><td><p>1-2个</p></td><td><p>容量不超过100Wh（27000mAh）</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>转换插头</p></td><td><p>2个</p></td><td><p>泰国为双扁脚A型，220V</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>耳机</p></td><td><p>1副</p></td><td><p>飞机、长途车使用</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>相机及配件</p></td><td><p>按需</p></td><td><p>备用电池、存储卡</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>自拍杆</p></td><td><p>1个</p></td><td><p>部分景点禁止使用</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h3><strong>支付方式准备</strong></h3><h4><strong>现金管理</strong></h4><div class=\"hyc-common-markdown__table-wrapper isDark\" data-has-scroll=\"false\"><table><thead><tr><th><p>货币类型</p></th><th><p>建议金额</p></th><th><p>兑换渠道</p></th><th><p>存放建议</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>泰铢现金</p></td><td><p>10,000-15,000铢/人</p></td><td><p>国内银行预约</p></td><td><p>分多处存放</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>人民币备用</p></td><td><p>2,000-3,000元</p></td><td><p>携带少量</p></td><td><p>应急使用</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>小面额泰铢</p></td><td><p>准备100铢以下</p></td><td><p>到泰后立即兑换</p></td><td><p>支付小费、车费</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h4><strong>银行卡选择</strong></h4><ul class=\"ybc-ul-component\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>💳 <strong>信用卡</strong>：Visa/Mastercard，建议带2张不同银行</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>💳 <strong>储蓄卡</strong>：带银联标识，支持境外取现</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>📱 <strong>电子支付</strong>：</p><ul class=\"ybc-ul-component\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>支付宝：大型商场、连锁店可用</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>微信支付：部分中国游客多的商家接受</p></span></li></ul></span></li></ul><h3><strong>常用药品清单</strong></h3><div class=\"hyc-common-markdown__table-wrapper isDark\" data-has-scroll=\"false\"><table><thead><tr><th><p>类别</p></th><th><p>药品名称</p></th><th><p>用途说明</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>肠胃类</p></td><td><p>蒙脱石散、黄连素</p></td><td><p>预防水土不服、食物不适</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>感冒类</p></td><td><p>感冒冲剂、退烧药</p></td><td><p>应对空调房温差</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>防暑类</p></td><td><p>藿香正气水、清凉油</p></td><td><p>户外活动中暑预防</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>外伤类</p></td><td><p>创可贴、碘伏棉签、云南白药</p></td><td><p>小伤口处理</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>防蚊类</p></td><td><p>防蚊喷雾、青草膏、蚊虫叮咬药</p></td><td><p>必备，清迈蚊虫多</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>个人特殊药</p></td><td><p>按需准备</p></td><td><p>过敏药、慢性病药物</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h3><strong>出发前3分钟检查</strong></h3><ol class=\"ybc-ol-component ybc-ol-component_1\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>🔌 <strong>家中安全</strong>：关闭水电燃气、门窗锁好</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>📱 <strong>电子设备</strong>：手机充电、下载离线地图、保存重要联系方式</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>📄 <strong>证件核对</strong>：护照、机票、酒店订单、保险单</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>💰 <strong>现金分装</strong>：分开放置，少量随身</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>🧳 <strong>行李确认</strong>：重量符合航空公司规定（通常经济舱20kg）</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>⏰ <strong>时间安排</strong>：提前3小时到达机场</p></span></li></ol><h3><strong>最后提醒</strong></h3><ul class=\"ybc-ul-component\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>📍 <strong>重要信息备份</strong>：</p><pre class=\"ybc-pre-component ybc-pre-component_not-math\"><code>酒店名称：[填写酒店英文名]\n酒店地址：[填写泰文地址]\n酒店电话：[填写联系方式]\n紧急联系人：[填写国内紧急联系人]\n中国驻清迈总领馆：+66-53-280380\n旅游警察：1155</code></pre></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>📱 <strong>手机设置</strong>：</p><ul class=\"ybc-ul-component\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>开通国际漫游（接收短信免费）</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>下载Grab（打车）、Google Maps、翻译软件</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>保存大使馆、保险公司紧急电话</p></span></li></ul></span></li></ul><hr style=\"margin: 40px 0; border: none; border-top: 3px solid #667eea; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); height: 3px; border-radius: 2px;\"><h1>二、 🛂 签证攻略</h1><h3><strong>当前签证政策（2024年更新）</strong></h3><div class=\"hyc-common-markdown__table-wrapper isDark\" data-has-scroll=\"false\"><table><thead><tr><th><p>签证类型</p></th><th><p>停留期限</p></th><th><p>申请方式</p></th><th><p>所需材料</p></th><th><p>费用</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>免签入境</p></td><td><p>30天</p></td><td><p>抵达后直接入境</p></td><td><p>护照、返程机票、酒店订单</p></td><td><p>免费</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>旅游签证</p></td><td><p>60天</p></td><td><p>提前使馆办理</p></td><td><p>护照、照片、申请表等</p></td><td><p>240元</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>落地签</p></td><td><p>15天</p></td><td><p>机场办理</p></td><td><p>护照、照片、返程机票等</p></td><td><p>2000铢</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h3><strong>免签入境具体要求</strong></h3><ol class=\"ybc-ol-component ybc-ol-component_1\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>护照有效期</strong>：至少6个月以上</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>返程机票</strong>：30天内离开泰国的机票订单</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>住宿证明</strong>：覆盖全部行程的酒店预订单</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>资金证明</strong>：个人2万泰铢/家庭4万泰铢（抽查）</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>填写入境卡</strong>：飞机上或入境处填写TM.6表格</p></span></li></ol><h3><strong>电子入境卡（TM6）填写指南</strong></h3><ol class=\"ybc-ol-component ybc-ol-component_1\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>填写时间</strong>：出发前72小时内在线填写</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>官方网址</strong>：<a href=\"https://tm6.immigration.go.th/\">https://tm6.immigration.go.th</a></p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>所需信息</strong>：</p><ul class=\"ybc-ul-component\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>护照信息</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>航班信息</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>泰国住宿地址</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>联系方式</p></span></li></ul></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>保存凭证</strong>：填写完成后保存二维码，入境时出示</p></span></li></ol><hr style=\"margin: 40px 0; border: none; border-top: 3px solid #667eea; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); height: 3px; border-radius: 2px;\"><h1>三、 ✈️ 清迈机场入境流程</h1><h3><strong>清迈国际机场布局</strong></h3><pre class=\"ybc-pre-component ybc-pre-component_not-math\"><code>国际到达层（1楼）\n├── 移民检查柜台（Passport Control）\n├── 行李提取转盘（Baggage Claim）\n├── 海关检查（Customs）\n└── 到达大厅（Arrival Hall）</code></pre><h3><strong>详细入境步骤</strong></h3><p><strong>第一步：下飞机后</strong></p><ul class=\"ybc-ul-component\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>跟随“Arrivals”（到达）标识</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>准备护照、登机牌、入境卡</p></span></li></ul><p><strong>第二步：移民检查</strong></p><ul class=\"ybc-ul-component\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>选择“Foreign Passport”（外国护照）通道</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>提交护照、入境卡、返程机票</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>配合拍照、按指纹</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>领取盖章后的护照</p></span></li></ul><p><strong>第三步：领取行李</strong></p><ul class=\"ybc-ul-component\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>查看显示屏找到航班对应的行李转盘</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>确认行李无误</p></span></li></ul><p><strong>第四步：海关检查</strong></p><ul class=\"ybc-ul-component\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>无申报物品走绿色通道</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>有需申报物品走红色通道</p></span></li></ul><p><strong>第五步：到达大厅</strong></p><ul class=\"ybc-ul-component\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>兑换少量泰铢（应急用）</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>购买电话卡</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>选择交通方式前往市区</p></span></li></ul><h3><strong>注意事项</strong></h3><p>⚠️ <strong>禁止携带物品</strong>：新鲜水果、肉制品、毒品、盗版商品</p><p>⚠️ <strong>免税额度</strong>：个人用品总值不超过2万泰铢</p><p>⚠️ <strong>现金申报</strong>：携带超过2万美元需申报</p><hr style=\"margin: 40px 0; border: none; border-top: 3px solid #667eea; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); height: 3px; border-radius: 2px;\"><h1>四、 📱 电话卡与网络</h1><h3><strong>三大运营商对比</strong></h3><div class=\"hyc-common-markdown__table-wrapper isDark\" data-has-scroll=\"false\"><table><thead><tr><th><p>运营商</p></th><th><p>推荐套餐</p></th><th><p>价格</p></th><th><p>网络覆盖</p></th><th><p>特点</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>AIS</strong>​</p></td><td><p>Tourist SIM 8天</p></td><td><p>299铢</p></td><td><p>清迈全境优秀</p></td><td><p>信号最强，山区覆盖好</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>dtac</strong>​</p></td><td><p>Happy Tourist SIM</p></td><td><p>299铢</p></td><td><p>市区优秀</p></td><td><p>性价比高，游客首选</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>TrueMove</strong>​</p></td><td><p>Tourist SIM</p></td><td><p>299铢</p></td><td><p>市区良好</p></td><td><p>套餐灵活，充值方便</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h3><strong>购买与激活流程</strong></h3><ol class=\"ybc-ol-component ybc-ol-component_1\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>购买地点</strong>：机场到达厅运营商柜台</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>所需材料</strong>：护照（需要登记）</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>激活步骤</strong>：</p><ul class=\"ybc-ul-component\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>店员帮忙安装SIM卡</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>注册个人信息</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>选择套餐并支付</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>等待激活短信（约15分钟）</p></span></li></ul></span></li></ol><h3><strong>网络设置</strong></h3><ul class=\"ybc-ul-component\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>APN设置</strong>：通常自动设置，如需手动：</p><pre class=\"ybc-pre-component ybc-pre-component_not-math\"><code>AIS：APN=internet\ndtac：APN=www.dtac.co.th\nTrueMove：APN=internet</code></pre></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>余额查询</strong>：</p><ul class=\"ybc-ul-component\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>AIS：拨打*121#</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>dtac：拨打*101 * 9#</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p>TrueMove：拨打*123#</p></span></li></ul></span></li></ul><hr style=\"margin: 40px 0; border: none; border-top: 3px solid #667eea; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); height: 3px; border-radius: 2px;\"><h1>五、 🚗 机场至市区交通</h1><h3><strong>酒店信息准备</strong></h3><pre class=\"ybc-pre-component ybc-pre-component_not-math\"><code>英文名称：[填写酒店英文名]\n泰文地址：[填写完整泰文地址]\n联系电话：[填写酒店电话]\n预订确认号：[填写预订编号]</code></pre><h3><strong>交通方式详细对比</strong></h3><div class=\"hyc-common-markdown__table-wrapper isDark\" data-has-scroll=\"false\"><table><thead><tr><th><p>交通方式</p></th><th><p>价格范围</p></th><th><p>行程时间</p></th><th><p>适合人群</p></th><th><p>预订方式</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>机场出租车</strong>​</p></td><td><p>150-200铢</p></td><td><p>15-20分钟</p></td><td><p>家庭、行李多</p></td><td><p>机场柜台排队</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Grab网约车</strong>​</p></td><td><p>120-180铢</p></td><td><p>15-25分钟</p></td><td><p>年轻人、熟练APP用户</p></td><td><p>Grab应用程序</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>双条车</strong>​</p></td><td><p>50-100铢/人</p></td><td><p>20-30分钟</p></td><td><p>背包客、体验当地</p></td><td><p>机场外路边</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>酒店接送</strong>​</p></td><td><p>300-500铢</p></td><td><p>15-20分钟</p></td><td><p>首次到访、夜间到达</p></td><td><p>提前邮件预约</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h3><strong>各区域参考时间</strong></h3><ul class=\"ybc-ul-component\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>到古城</strong>：15-20分钟，约150铢</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>到宁曼路</strong>：10-15分钟，约120铢</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>到杭东区</strong>：25-30分钟，约250铢</p></span></li></ul><h3><strong>Grab使用指南</strong></h3><ol class=\"ybc-ol-component ybc-ol-component_1\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>下载注册</strong>：国内提前下载，用泰国手机号注册</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>支付方式</strong>：绑定信用卡或选择现金支付</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>输入地址</strong>：使用英文或泰文地址</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>选择车型</strong>：GrabCar（轿车）、GrabBike（摩托车）</p></span></li><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ol\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span class=\"ybc-li-component_content\"><p><strong>等待接驾</strong>：司机通常会通过APP内置翻译沟通</p></span></li></ol><hr style=\"margin: 40px 0; border: none; border-top: 3px solid #667eea; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); height: 3px; border-radius: 2px;\"><h1>六、 🏥 旅行保险推荐</h1><h3><strong>保险选择标准</strong></h3><ul class=\"ybc-ul-component\"><li class=\"ybc-li-component ybc-li-component_ul\"><span class=\"ybc-li-component__dot-wp\"></span><span